{"tid":1875760,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"線上授課","createTime":"2020-02-12T03:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T03:40:05.000Z","uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"163375bfeacc15b01b83ddf1b88966a1c55f75e1","tid":1875760,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100002644147891/posts/2575519202546193/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100002644147891%2Fposts%2F2575519202546193%2F%3F&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=e06232ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100002644147891/posts/2575519202546193/?</a><br />\n<br />\n由於封城，於是老共教育部門下令，要求孩子一律改線上授課，結果授課的老師下課後，螢幕關了，麥克風沒關，也沒下線，於是線上的孩子就默默的參與了實境秀&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n要看記得音量開小點，據說那一堂的授課率，是全員到齊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n#別誤會人家是在治病"},{"pid":"175f69d0912bc293a81cb455bfe77583843fb820","tid":1875760,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}